Package org.xandercat.pmdb.dto

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationAttribute
    Class to represent a generic dated application attribute.
    CloudUserSearchResults
    Class for storing cloud user synchronization information.
    CollectionPermission
    Class to represent the permission a user has for a movie collection.
    FormattedMovie
    Decorator class for Movie that adds formatting of attribute values for sort and display in the user interface.
    Movie
    Class to represent a movie and it's associated attributes.
    MovieCollection
    Class for representing a movie collection.
    PmdbUser
    User class that also doubles as UserDetails for Spring security.
    PmdbUserCredentials
    Lightweight user credentials class for storage in cloud.
